VLAN erstellen

Router:
interface GigabitEthernet0/0/1
encapsulation dot1Q <VLAN Nummer>
ipv6 address 2001:db8:<VLAN Nummer>::1/64
no shutdown

interface GigabitEthernet0/0/1
encapsulation dot1Q <VLAN Nummer>
ipv6 address 2001:db8:<VLAN Nummer>::1/64
no shutdown

Switch:
enable
conf t
vlan 10
name vlanHH10
exit
interface Gi0/2
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10
exit

interface Gi0/2
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 20
exit


interface Gi0/1/0
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20

end
write memory
